lead_paragraph: Haru Nomura of Japan survived windy conditions and a mid-round meltdown to claim her second win of the season, a four-shot victory at Swinging Skirts LPGA Classic in San Francisco on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Nomura Claims Four-Shot Win at Swinging Skirts LPGA Classic
